    "More details about the eROSITA point-source number density maps are presented in Liu et al. (2024).",
    "In this section, we present the point-source number count distributions averaged in a few wide Galactic latitude ranges.We divide the hemisphere into four Galactic latitude levels, 0-10 •, 10-20 •, 20-40 •, and 40-90 •.",
